## Daily groundwater levels for Sarah and Andrea
```{r}
a <- readNWISuv(siteNumbers = "182549066304300", 
                parameterCd = "72019",
                startDate = "2023-01-01", endDate = "2023-12-31",
               )
```

```{r}
write_csv(x = a, file = "./data_sarah.csv")
```


## Climate/weather data for Nora and Jasper
