## Climate/weather data for Sarah and Andrea
```{r}
aoi2use <- aoi_get(x = c(18.4280860241805, -66.5114494792146, 0.5,0.5))
```

```{r}
raster_chirps <- dap( 
  #URL = "https://coastwatch.pfeg.noaa.gov/erddap/griddap/chirps20GlobalDailyP05",
  #URL = "https://upwell.pfeg.noaa.gov/erddap/griddap/chirps20GlobalAnnualP05",
  URL = "https://upwell.pfeg.noaa.gov/erddap/griddap/chirps20GlobalDailyP05",
  catalog = NULL,
  AOI = aoi2use,#cambodia_pt,
  grid = NULL,
  varname = NULL, 
  startDate = "2023-01-01",
  endDate = "2023-12-31", 
  toptobottom = F,
  verbose = TRUE
)
```


